room_title: Escape room "HouDoneIt?" by My Greatest Escape in Ventura
room_address: 15500 W Telegraph Rd #15 Santa Paula, CA 93060
room_description:
In the early 1900’s it was believed that a famous escape artist died from an unfortunate injury. However, new evidence suggests that he did not die from those injuries, but in fact, continued to perform for years to come, and was subsequently murdered. Thanks to the invention of time travel, we can now go back in time and solve old crimes. 
You have signed up with a new detective agency called M.A.G.I.C.: Magician’s Alliance Gathering Intelligence Center. Your mission, travel back in time and solve this case… This first part of your journey is like a typical escape, the second part, you are playing the game of Clue by finding evidence and eliminating suspects, weapons, and motives. You have 60 minutes to find the clues and solve the mystery, before time runs out. Do you have what it takes?
